	e is a Wednesday night showcase featuring alumni from Unexpected Productio
	ns Improv School. Each performance highlights a different alumni group\\\,
	 putting their training to the test with unpredictable scenes\\\, various 
	formats\\\, and improvised stories. From long-form storytelling to charact
	er work\\\, these performers explore the boundaries of improv. \\nJan 7 Ma
	rket Improv \\nJan 14 \\nJan 21 \\nBut the fun doesn’t stop there! Stick a
	round for a double feature as we roll into Seattle’s longest-running Impro
	v Open Mic: the Duos Open Mic! Starting at 8:00 pm\\\, this weekly showcas
	e promises even more laughs\\\, surprises\\\, and improv magic.\n\nhttps:/
